These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
House: townhouse, gothic-revival
There are 2 different favourite colors: aquamarine, turquise
1. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the left of the person who likes aquamarine##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| House           | gothic-revival | townhouse |
| Color   | turquise     | aquamarine  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: apricot, brown
2 different games are played: bridge, canasta
1. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the left of the person who likes apricot##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Color         | brown   | apricot      |
| Game   | bridge | canasta |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, november
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: sports, crime
1. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the right of the person watching sports movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| Birthday   | november | march    |
| Movie-Genre     | sports | crime |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-4::.
2 different pets are kept: dog, cat
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: marigold, begonia
1. the person who growsbegonia is somewhere to the right of the owner of the dog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |
| Pet   | dog   | cat |
| Flower   | marigold | begonia |

 #################################

 
